divs: Sighting Detailsi was in my garden taking photos of the sky and did not notice anything in picture till i uploaded them on to my computer. took 2 pictures with in 20 seconds of each other, one showed nothing the other had what looks like a matalic craft in it with the sun reflected off it on one side.
